node.text: Still so surreal to me that I’m a part of this wonderful group of women and am so excited to welcome @clarecrawley into our “Club of Bachelorettes”  We filmed this forever ago during quarantine so just pretend like you’re watching it back in March. Don’t blink or you might miss me and three of my four! Sending you all the love and prayers tonight, Clare! ❤️❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Emily Maynard Johnson on August 16, 2021 tagging @rickihendrick111. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: my days of hearing what’s on my girls heart on the drive home from school are over. it feels like she went from 5 years old to driving in the blink of an eye and even though I’ve been crying on demand all day, I’m so happy for her and her new found freedom. It’s a big day for you, Ki, and I’m so excited for you.  I’m also excited thinking about all the money I’m going to save on Postmates. I love you all the way to Heaven. ❤️

node.text: Is it normal to sit in the parking lot after camp drop off, looking at pictures and missing them already? {ages 3,4, and 5}

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Emily Maynard Johnson on July 09, 2021 tagging @rickihendrick111, and @grandbohemiancharlotte. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: this girl. I have put off doing her birthday post because I just don’t have the words to describe how special of a soul she is. she is kind beyond belief, thoughtful, grace filled, sensitive, low key the funniest person I know, laid back since day 1, and just so naturally cool without even trying. she also has more grit and wisdom than most people double her age. life has thrown her some tough blows but she keeps on going with a smile on her face and Jesus in her heart. Ricki, you are beautiful inside and out and I’m just so happy that God picked me to be your mommy. You are more precious than all the rubies! ❤️🤟🏻

node.text:
Our family has grown and so has our passion for @levinechildrens. With 5 kids, it’s reassuring to know we have a world-class children’s hospital right here in Charlotte.
Please join me and lots of others who love kids on April 10 for a fun, safe Night at the Drive-In! Go to the link in my bio for tickets before they sell out! {📸 @arianaclarestudio }
